descriptionMarkdown:
This is an updated version of an older blueprint, I added a few missing items and uranium production.

It crafts everything except for science packs (over 120 different items in total)

Including belts, inserters, bots, ammunition, etc...

Constructive critique is appreciated ;-)

Input:

        90 iron ore per sec     
        30 copper ore per sec
        30 stone per sec
        15 coal per sec
        15 uranium per sec
        160 oil per sec
        water

Edit: Added a few buffer chests.
        Smoothed a few things out so it doesn't look as messy.
        Removed and replaced some of the wiring
title: Everything you need (1.0 Mall, crafts over 120 different items from ores to endproducts)
